
---
# **AI Document Summarizer**

An end-to-end full-stack application that allows users to upload documents (PDF, TXT, DOCX), automatically summarize them using AI models, and manage authentication (login/register) through a secure backend.
This project contains a **React + Vite frontend** and a **FastAPI backend**, with optional Docker support.

---

## ğŸš€ **Features**

* ğŸ” User Authentication (Register/Login)
