* ğŸ¤– AI-powered text summarization
* ğŸ¦ Document processing history (optional)
* ğŸ“¡ REST API built with FastAPI
* ğŸ¨ Modern UI with React, TailwindCSS, and Vite
* ğŸ³ Docker support for easy deployment

